{"tid":1845392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［笑撚死我第一滴血］終於有第一個支那共產黨黨狗死","createTime":"2020-01-27T06:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T14:09:12.000Z","uid":164590,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5d33fee58a89b1802df7ec6f1ae660eff6ccc84d","tid":1845392,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:39:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://today.line.me/HK/article/7WlPGl?utm_source=copyshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Farticle%2F7WlPGl%3Futm_source%3Dcopyshare&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RvRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=505e988b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/HK/article/7WlPGl?utm_source=copyshare</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢市官員感染武漢肺炎去世<br />\n另外，財新網報道，武漢市民族宗教事務委員會前主任、正局級官員王獻良，昨日下午因感染武漢肺炎搶救無效去世，終年62歲。這是第一位感染武漢肺炎去世的當地官員。王獻良2012年起擔任武漢市民宗委主任，及後因為多次違反中央八項規定精神被問責，被免去主任職務，之後他仍在民宗委內任職。<br />\n守護言論與新聞自由。立場新聞，寸步不退。<br />\n每月贊助支持立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n定係其實已經死咗好多個啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8659a77cc107e499e6adf0e991ec850610f8fbc","tid":1845392,"uid":339172,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:40:19.000Z","msg":"牛逼死了"},{"pid":"04f0079fd25359a29fa63669423b4f9343f990b4","tid":1845392,"uid":138232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:40:22.000Z","msg":"幾時卜下中國疫情<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2d51ea20a90777c6b1153343646beff36d2372","tid":1845392,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:40:33.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"dc6b8a75809108a3bef40fc8f8e9960209dd759c","tid":1845392,"uid":164590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"04f0079fd25359a29fa63669423b4f9343f990b4","tid":1845392,"uid":138232